.TH LOA-IMPORT 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
import \- Import books from JSON or CSV
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> import
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for file path and format if needed.
.TP
Skips duplicates and reports added/skipped/invalid entries.
.TP
JSON imports can optionally apply goals and reading list metadata.
.TP
Metadata import also supports smart lists and smart reading interests profile.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> import
